How to Run
Make sure Python 3 is installed on your system.
Save the code as chatbot.py.
Open a terminal or command prompt.
Run the program:
python chatbot.py
 Supported Commands
User Input	Chatbot Response
hello	Hi there!
hi	Hello!
good morning	Good morning! Have a great day!
good evening	Good evening!
how are you	I'm fine, thanks!
what is your name	My name is ChatBot.
who made you	I was created using Python.
what can you do	I can chat with you and answer simple questions.
tell me a joke	Displays a simple joke
favorite color	I like blue because it looks cool on screens!
thank you	You're welcome!
time	Shows current system time
date	Shows today's date
bye	Ends the chat session
